These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-1::.
There 2 different types of food: onion, orange
There are 2 different favourite colors: black, turquise
1. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
2. the person eating onion is not to the right of the person who likes turquise##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |
| Food        | onion   | orange   |
| Color   | turquise | black |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, soy-milk
The people have 2 different jobs:  manager, doctor
1. the manager is not to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##8
2. the manager is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | juice   |
| Job      | doctor | manager |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-3::.
There 2 different types of food: cabbage, peach
The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, chess
1. the person eating cabbage is not to the left of the person who's hobby is chess##8
2. the person eating peach is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Food          | peach | cabbage |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks   | chess     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-4::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: poppy, lily
2 different pets are kept: dog, fish
1. the owner of the dog is not to the right of the person who growspoppy##8
2. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |
| Flower   | lily | poppy |
| Pet    | dog    | fish |

